Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yatumye habaho iterambere ry'akarere, kandi umubare w'abanduye icyorezo cya coronavirus mu bindi bihugu ku isi uragenda wiyongera nk'uko byagenze mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) yatangaje icyorezo cya COVID-19 nk'icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, nk'uko Eurosurveillance 2020 ibivuga, Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje ko ari bo bantu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi nk'uko byemejwe na OMS.
Mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye batangajwe ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bagarutse baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 babonetse mu bihugu byose 30 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza ubu hamaze kuboneka abantu 39,768 banduye, harimo n'abapfuye 1,727, muri bo 17,750 banduye n'abapfuye 1,441 mu Butaliyani gusa.
Kubona imibare y'abamaze kwandura no kwiyongera kw'abanduye COVID-19
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara (ECDC), gitanga imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose byo ku isi, biva gusa mu makuru y'ibiro by'ubuzima by'ibihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'akarere na OMS, kandi bigaruka buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 iteye mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza no kuyigereranya n'u Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo kureba uko ibikorwa bya COVID-19 byagiye bihinduka, twasuzumye imibare y'ibyumweru 14 by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 kugira ngo turebe uko ibihe bya COVID-19 byagiye byihindura muri buri gihugu cya EU n'Ubwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twatangaje kandi imibare y'abanduye muri buri gihugu cyacu ku isaha ya 8:00 za mu gitondo ku ya 15 Werurwe, ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe.
Imibare ya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza
Imibare y'ibyumweru 14 by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, muri rusange ihuje n'iy'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Mu bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza muri rusange, umubare w'abandura COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ku ya 21 Gashyantare, maze ugera ku kigero cyo hejuru ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibikoresho by'ibanze).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye cyane mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza na byo byerekanye ko byiyongereye mu mibare y'abanduye COVID-19.
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'amezi 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibi byerekana ko saa munani za mu gitondo z'itariki ya 15 Werurwe, umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu 15 by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza wari ungana n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu bishize cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza wiyongereye cyane.
Imiterere igaragara y'ibipimo by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 yerekana ko iyi ndwara y'ibyorezo igenda yiyongera ku muvuduko nk'uwo mu bihugu byose.
Ibi ni mu gihe ibihugu biri mu bihe bitandukanye kandi bitandukanye mu buryo bw'ubuzima rusange, mu buryo bwo gusobanura indwara no mu buryo bwo gupima abarwayi kugira ngo hamenyekane niba baranduye COVID-19.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu duce twanduye tw'u Butaliyani basobanuye ko hafi 10% by'abarwaye COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bwihariye, kandi amakuru yatangajwe n'ibitangazamakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bwihariye muri utwo turere byageze ku rwego rwo hejuru.
Amakuru y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwariye mu bitaro no mu bigo byita ku barwayi ba mu mutwe mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi ubu agaragara ku kigero cya 6% na 1% by'abarwayi (amakuru ntabwo agaragazwa).
Ariko kandi, ibi bikoresho bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo amakuru y'ubugenzuzi bugezweho yibanda ku mubare w'abanduye n'abapfuye ashobore kuzuzwa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Ugushyingo 2010 bugaragaza itandukaniro rikomeye mu mubare w'ibitanda byo kwa muganga bikorerwa mu bitaro byagutse n'ibikorerwa mu bigo by'ubuvuzi by'ibanze mu Burayi, aho umubare w'ibitanda by'indembe mu Budage ari 29.2 naho muri Portugal ari 4.2 ku bantu 100,000.
Ibi byerekana ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite ibikoresho bike cyangwa byinshi ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani (ibitanda 12.5 by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe na serivisi z'ubuvuzi bw'indembe kuri 100,000 mu Gushyingo 2020).
Ibimenyetso by'imiterere bifitanye isano no kurenza ubushobozi bwo kwita ku buzima, hamwe n'ibipimo by'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'uburayi n'ubwongereza ku bijyanye n'ubwiyongere bw'ibyago byo kurara kubera COVID-19 bifitanye isano n'ibyago birenze 90% byo kwiyongera kw'ubushobozi bw'ibitanda by'indembe, byerekanwe mu isesengura rya gatandatu rya ECDC ku byerekeye ibyago bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko hari umubare munini w'abarwayi mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'uburayi n'ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane bikorera abaturage bo mu karere runaka, amakuru ajyanye n'abarwayi n'ibitanda by'indembe biba byiza cyane kuyakura mu magambo y'ibigo by'akarere ku rwego rwa 2 (2-NUTS) imibare.
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ibindi bihugu bigaragaza ko COVID-19 ikwirakwira cyane mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi ba mu bitaro byagombye kwitegura uko coronavirus ya SARS-CoV-2 yakomeza kwanduzwa mu baturage ndetse n'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongera, bagakenera kwitabwaho, bamwe muri bo bakaba bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, nk'uko biri mu bice by'Ubutaliyani byanduye.
Nkuko byagaragajwe na raporo ya vuba y'icyerekezo cy'ibyago bya ECDC, uburyo bwuzuye, bugira ingufu kandi bwihuse burakenewe mu guhagarika ikwirakwira rya coronavirus ya 2-SARS-COV, hamwe no guhindura uburyo bwo guhagarika no kugabanya, kuko umubare w'abanduye ugenda wiyongera vuba, ntabwo igihe gihagije kiboneka ku bashinzwe gufata ibyemezo n'ibitaro kugirango basobanukirwe, bahindure kandi bahindure ibisubizo byabo igihe bishoboka.
Igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago hamwe n'ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zigamije kumenya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
