Imyaka: Imyaka ni yo mpamvu ikomeye cyane mu gihe cyo gukira SARS, kimwe na COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane abantu bafite imyaka 65-30 kandi mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 8,866, 47,7% by'abarwayi bari bafite imyaka irenga 50 nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru.
Abarwayi bari bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane n'abaganga bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara izindi ndwara kandi bari bafite imyaka myinshi kurusha abandi (umwanya w'imyaka 66 ugereranyije na 51), ibyo bikaba byerekana ko imyaka ari yo ahanini ituma abantu barwara COVID-19 barwara.
Igitsina: SARS-CoV-2 yibasira abagabo cyane kurusha abagore (0.31/100,000 ugereranyije na 0.27/100,000), nk'uko byavuzwe mbere.
Ubundi burwayi: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane n'abaganga bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara umutima cyangwa kugira ibibazo by'umutima.
Ibyago by'umutima kandi ni byo bituma abantu benshi bapfa kubera SARS.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gutera collagicity ku ngirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri z'indwara ya ACE2 zishobora gutera indwara y'igifu mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ni ngombwa kuvuga ko imyaka n'uburwayi bw'ibanze bifitanye isano kandi bishobora guhura.
Ibimenyetso bidasanzwe: Igipimo cya poroteyine y'umusemburo wa C (CRP) mu maraso kigaragaza ubukana bw'indwara cyangwa kwangirika kw'ingingo kandi ni ikimenyetso cy'uburwayi, gusubiza imiti, no gukira burundu.
Hari kandi n'ibipimo bya CRP byerekana isano iri hagati y'uburemere n'ubwirinzi bwa COVID-19.
Byongeye kandi, kuzamuka kwa lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT) na creatine kinase (CK) bishobora gufasha mu kwemeza ibisubizo.
Izi enzymes ziboneka cyane mu ngingo nyinshi z'umubiri, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu myanya y'ubuhumekero, kandi zisohoka mu gihe imyakura yangiritse.
Ibyo byose bizasohorera ku buyobe n'ubugome.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'ubuvuzi: Kugira ngo hategerezwe ingaruka n'ibibazo bya COVID-19, hagomba gufatwa ibipimo by'igituza n'ihindagurika ry'ibipimo by'ubuvuzi hamwe n'ibindi bibazo.
Gukoresha Steroids: Nkuko byavuzwe mbere, Steroids zangiza ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri kandi akenshi zikorwa nk'umuti wunganira mu kuvura indwara ziterwa n'indwara zo mu mutwe kugirango bigabanure ibyago by'indwara.
Kubera ko ingano y'indwara ya corticosteroids yari yiganje mu barwayi ba SARS, abenshi mu barokotse bagaragaje ko bahitanwa n'urupfu rw'amagufwa n'uburwayi bwo mu maraso, hamwe n'ubumuga no kutagira ubuzima bwiza.
Ku bw'ibyo, ni ngombwa ko abarwayi ba COVID-19 bahabwa imiti ya Steroid ku rugero ruciriritse kandi mu gihe gito.
