Icyitonderwa Nubwo COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu buzajya buhinduka buhoro buhoro dushingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi; bityo rero, ingamba zo gusuzuma no kuvura zigenda zihindurwa.
Urugero, amabwiriza yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 yasohowe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abanyamerika (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020, yasohoye imibare irindwi yose hamwe n'ibisobanuro bimwe byahindutse cyane.
Ubu ubuyobozi dufite ni amagambo yavuzwe na Zhou et al. Hut, batanze igitekerezo cyoroshye cyo gutanga amanota ku buhanga bwabo mu buvuzi.
Ibikorwa byabo byatanze igihamya gishya cyerekana ko ubuyobozi bwacu ari bwo bufite imbaraga zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Turashyigikira umurimo w'ingenzi bakora kandi turabashimira.
Ariko kandi, akazi kabo gakeneye kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya yo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (igerageza rya karindwi) n'ubushakashatsi bushya.
Nk'uko byemejwe n'ibya 7 (ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo umuntu akemure ikibazo cy'uburwayi, agomba guhuza ibintu bibiri by'ingenzi by'amateka y'icyorezo n'ibintu bibiri by'ibimenyetso by'uburwayi kugira ngo ashobore gukora isesengura ryuzuye, cyangwa se agomba kuba afite ibintu bitatu by'ibimenyetso by'uburwayi niba amateka y'icyorezo adahwitse:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) Amateka y'urugendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho abantu bagaragayeho COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (2) Amateka y'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 (binyuze mu gupima aside ya nucleic positive); (3) Amateka y'ubwandu bw'abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero mu mujyi wa Wuhan no mu turere tuwukikije, cyangwa mu yindi miryango aho COVID-19 yavuzwe mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (4) Amateka y'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bw'ubwoko bumwe na bumwe bwemejwe (>=2 abanduye na/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bufite ubwandu bwa polio mu gihe cy'ibyumweru 2 mu duce duto, nk'amazu, ibiro, amashuri, n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi: (1) ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero; (2) ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso twera, cyangwa umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso mu gihe cy'intangiriro.
Gushakisha icyemezo cy'uburwayi bugomba gushingira ku kibazo gikekwaho ko hari ibimenyetso by'indwara cyangwa ibimenyetso bya serolojiya: (1) igisubizo cya PCR cy'igihe cya vuba cya SARS-CoV-2; (2) urutonde rwuzuye rwa virusi rwerekana inkomoko ikomeye ya coronavirus nshya; (3) igisubizo cy'indwara yihariye ya IgM na IgG kuri SARS-CoV-2 mu isuzuma rya serum; cyangwa ihinduka ry'indwara yihariye ya IgG ya SARS-CoV-2 kuva ku mbi kugeza ku nziza, cyangwa se umubare => 4 mu gihe cyo gukira hejuru y'icyiciro cy'indwara.
Dushobora kubona ko ibizamini bya PCR by'igihe nyacyo bya nucleic acid mu nzira y'ubuhumekero cyangwa ibipimo by'amaraso byongerewe ku gice cya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) no ku gice cya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Ibimenyetso by'indwara byongerewe mu cyiciro cya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) n'icya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma ibimenyetso bya serolojiya byongerewe mu cya karindwi.
Ibi byakozwe bishingiye ku gikorwa gikomeje gukorwa n'abashakashatsi cyo gushaka igikoresho cyo gupima aside ya nucleic cy'ubushakashatsi bwihuse, hamwe n'ibipimo by'ubuhumekero birimo n'ibipimo by'amaraso, byongereye ibisubizo by'ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi bifasha gutanga ibisubizo byiza bya antibody yihariye mu bipimo byemejwe.
Byongeye kandi, hari ibimenyetso byinshi kandi byinshi byerekana ko ari ngombwa kwitondera indwara zidakunze kugaragaza ibimenyetso n'indwara zitagaragaza ibimenyetso.
Ku bw'ibyo, imibare ya Zhou et al. yagombaga kuvugururwa, kuko bagaragaje ko umuntu udafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi ari "ubw'ibyago bike".
Uburyo bwo gutanga amanota bugomba kandi gusuzumwa mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi no mu bindi byigwa.
Kubera iyo mpamvu, twizeye ko hari ibindi bimenyetso bifatika bizatangwa kandi turasaba abasomyi gutanga ibitekerezo byabo.
Mu gihe hari "ubwandu bukekwaho" cyangwa "ubwandu bwemejwe", turasaba abantu gukurikiza amabwiriza mashya y'ibihugu byabo.
Itsinda ryacu rizajya risubiramo amabwiriza yacu mu gihe gikwiriye kugira ngo ritange ubufasha.
