Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi.
Ku wa Gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 - indwara iterwa na coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 - ari icyorezo ku isi.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku buryo indwara yageze aho ikwira, aho kugaragaza uko ibintu byihariye byifashe, OMS ishimangira ko ubutegetsi bugomba gufata ingamba:
Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, yavuze ko ibihugu byose bishobora guhindura icyerekezo cy'icyorezo.
Niba ibihugu byemera abaturage babyo, kubashakisha, kubakiza, kubatandukanya no kubakurikirana mu buryo bwo gusubiza.
Dufite impungenge zikomeye kubera ubukana n'ubukana bw'iki cyorezo.
Dr Tom Friedan, umuyobozi wa mbere w'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, yavuze ko icyorezo "kitari cyitezwe".
Yavuze ko, mu nyandiko yasohotse na CNN muri Gashyantare, "Uretse ibicurane, nta zindi virusi zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero zigeze zigaragazwa kuva zavutse kugeza aho zikwirakwizwa ku isi".
