Icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20 ni icyorezo gikomeje cy'indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19) iterwa n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero iterwa na coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2).
Iki cyorezo cyamenyekanye i Wuhan, mu Bushinwa mu kwezi kwa cumi na kumwe mu 2019, cyatangajwe ko ari ikibazo cy'uburwayi bw'abantu ku isi ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama 2020, kandi cyiswe icyorezo ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bihitana abagera ku 97.000.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 bakize.
Umubare w'abandura mu Bushinwa ugereranywa na 4%, mu gihe ku isi yose ugereranywa na 13.04% uhereye muri Algeria kugeza kuri 0.08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bisanzwe birimo kuribwa umutima, inkorora no guhumeka nabi.
Ibi bishobora gutuma indwara ikomera cyane, urugero nk'indwara y'ibihaha n'izindi ndwara zikomeye z'ubuhumekero.
Igihe cyo kuvurwa kugeza ibimenyetso bitangiye ni iminsi itanu, ariko bishobora gutwara iminsi ibiri kugeza kuri 14.
Nta rukingo cyangwa umuti wa virusi uzwi.
Gufata imiti ya mbere ni uburyo bwo kuvura ibimenyetso no gukemura ibibazo. Ingamba zasabwe n'abaganga harimo gukaraba intoki, gupfuka umunwa mu gihe ufite cocaine, kugendera kure abandi, no kwisuzumisha no kwicungira mu kato ku bantu bakekwaho kuba baranduye.
Ku isi hose, abayobozi bitabiriye bashyiraho ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo, gushyira mu kato, guhagarika ingendo, kugenzura ibyago by'abakozi, no gufunga ibigo.
Icyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye ry'ubukungu n'imibereho ku isi, gusubika cyangwa guhagarika ibikorwa bya siporo, amadini, politiki n'umuco, no kugabanya ibicuruzwa byinshi bitewe no kugura ibintu byinshi.
Amashuri na za kaminuza byafunzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa mu gihugu mu bihugu 193, bigira ingaruka ku bice bigera kuri 99.4% by'abanyeshuri ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo kuri virusi yakwirakwijwe kuri interineti, kandi hari ubwoba bw'abanyamahanga n'ivangura ku baturage b'Abashinwa, abandi bantu bo mu bwoko n'imiterere mu Burasirazuba no mu Majyepfo ashyira Uburasirazuba bw'Ubushinwa, n'abandi baturage bo mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Kubera ko ingendo zagabanutse kandi inganda nini zarafunzwe, habayeho kugabanuka kw'ibyuka bihumanya ikirere n'imyuka ihumanya ikirere.
