Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, bwagaragaje ko ingano y'iyo ndwara ari 5.7.
Abenshi mu barwaye COVID-19 barakira.
Ku bantu batabasha gukira, kuva ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara kugeza ku rupfu, bifata iminsi iri hagati ya 6 na 41, akenshi ni iminsi 14.
Kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97,000 bamaze guhitanwa na COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku ya 5 Gashyantare, 80% by'abapfuye bari abantu barengeje imyaka 60, kandi 75% bari bafite izindi ndwara zirimo indwara z'umutima na diyabete. Umubare w'abantu bapfuye bishwe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri rusange ni abapfuye basuzumwe bagasanga baranduye COVID-19 hakurikijwe amabwiriza yemewe.
Umubare nyawo w'abapfuye bazize COVID-19 ushobora kuba uri hejuru cyane, kuko ushobora kuba urimo abantu bapfuye batarafatwa - urugero nko mu bigo by'abarezi, n'ibindi.
Ibipimo bimwe na bimwe byo mu Butaliyani bigaragaza ko umubare w'abantu bapfuye muri iki cyorezo wikubye inshuro 4-5 umubare w'abapfuye bazize COVID-19.
Umuvugizi w'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yagize ati "tuzi ko [umubare w'abapfuye] ari muto cyane", itangazo riherekejwe n'ibyavuzwe ko umubare umwe utabarurwa muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika. Akenshi, uwo mubare muke uba mu gihe cy'ibyorezo, nk'icyorezo cy'ibicurane by'ingurube cya N1H1 cya 2009.
Umuntu wa mbere wapfuye hanze y'Ubushinwa yabonetse muri Filipine ku ya 1 Gashyantare, naho uwa mbere wapfuye hanze ya Aziya aboneka mu Bufaransa ku ya 14 Gashyantare.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, hanze y'Ubushinwa, hapfuye abantu barenga icumi na babiri, buri umwe muri Iran, Koreya y'Epfo n'u Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ibihugu birenga mirongo ine n'uturere byatangaje ko byahitanye abantu, ku migabane yose uretse Antarctica. Hari ingamba nyinshi zashyizweho mu kugabanya umubare w'abapfa.
Iyi mibare igenda ihinduka bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi bigira ingaruka ku mubare w'ibipimo, ubwiza bw'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kwivuza, igihe cy'indwara itangiriye, n'ibintu by'abaturage nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima rusange. Imibare y'urupfu igaragaza umubare w'abapfa bagabanyije umubare w'abanduye mu gihe runaka.
Dukurikije imibare ya Johns Hopkins University, umubare w'abamaze gupfa ku isi ni 6.0% (97,039/1,617,204) kugeza ku ya 10 Mata 2020.
Umubare uratandukanye bitewe n'akarere.
Mu Bushinwa, imibare y'urupfu iteganijwe yagabanutse iva kuri 17.3 (ku bantu batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso kuva ku ya 1-10 Mutarama 2020) * ijya kuri 0.7% (ku bantu batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso nyuma ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ibindi bipimo birimo igipimo cy'urupfu rw'ubwandu (CFR), kigaragaza igipimo cy'abantu banduye bapfa bazize indwara, n'igipimo cy'urupfu rw'abarwaye (IFR), kigaragaza igipimo cy'abantu banduye (bamaze kumenyekana n'abatarabyemezwa) bapfa bazize indwara.
Imibare ntabwo ihuje n'igihe kandi ikurikirana abaturage bafite ubwandu bwihariye binyuze mu kuvura.
Abahanga benshi bagerageje kubara imibare y'abantu ku giti cyabo.
Ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oxford gishinzwe ubuvuzi bushingiye ku bimenyetso gitanga icyizere cy'uko igipimo cy'urupfu rw'icyorezo muri rusange kiri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Ibipimo byo hejuru by'ibipimo byemeranya n'ibyavuye mu bipimo bya mbere bya COVID-19 byakozwe mu Budage, ndetse n'ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bw'ibarurishamibare busesengura ingaruka z'ibizamini ku bipimo bya CFR.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeza ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cyo kuzamuka n'igihe cy'iherezo cy'icyorezo ntabwo bizwi neza kandi bishobora guhinduka bitewe n'ahantu.
Massage Boni wo muri kaminuza ya Penn State yagize ati "Udashyize mu bikorwa ibizamini, ubwandu bw'icyorezo burushaho kwiyongera, hanyuma bugatangira kugabanuka igihe indwara itagikomeza kubaho.
Ariko nta muntu ushobora kumenya neza igihe ibyo bizabera. "
Umujyanama wa leta y'Ubushinwa mu by'ubuvuzi, Zhong Nashen, yavuze ko "birashoboka ko bizarangira muri Kamena" niba ibihugu byose byiteguye gukurikiza inama z'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ku ngamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kochersky wo muri Kaminuza y'u Bwongereza mu by'ubuvuzi bw'isuku n'ubushyuhe yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 "izamara imyaka imwe cyangwa ibiri".
Nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Imperial College, bwakozwe na Neil Ferguson, kwirinda no kwirinda abandi bantu bizakenerwa "kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse (hashobora kuba amezi 18 cyangwa arenga)".
William Schaffner wo muri Vanderbilt yagize ati "Ntekereza ko bishoboka ko coronavirus - kubera ko yandura cyane - itazongera kubaho" kandi "bikaba bishoboka ko izahinduka indwara y'igihe, igaruka buri mwaka".
Ibibazo byo kugaruka bihinduka bitewe n'uburyo bwo kurwanya no kwiyongera kw'impuzandengo y'isubira inyuma.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bitagaragara kandi abantu banduye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara ni uburibwe (88%) n'ikinya (68%).
Ibindi bimenyetso bidakunze kugaragara harimo kurwara ibicurane, guhumeka nabi, kubura uburyohe, guhumeka nabi, ububabare bw'imitsi n'ibice by'umubiri, kuribwa n'inshinge, kubabara, kugira iseseme, kugira iseseme, kugira iseseme, kuvira amaraso hamwe no kugira inkorora, igifu, cyangwa ubururu. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rivuga ko abantu bagera kuri batandatu barwara cyane kandi bafite ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ihindagurika nk'ibibazo byo guhumeka, ububabare cyangwa umuvuduko w'umuhogo uhoraho, gutakaza amazi mu buryo butunguranye, ingorane zo kugenda, no kugira ubururu mu maso cyangwa mu kanwa; kwitabwaho na muganga byihuse birakenewe niba ibi bimenyetso bihari. Gushyiraho izindi ndwara bishobora gutera indwara y'ibihaha ikomeye, umuvuduko ukabije w'ibihaha, uburozi mu maraso no gupfa.
Bamwe mu banduye bashobora kutagira ibimenyetso, nta bimenyetso by'uburwayi bafite ariko ibipimo byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi bagaragaje ko abantu bahuye cyane n'abantu banduye bagomba gukurikiranwa cyane no gukingirwa kugira ngo barinde ubwandu.
Ubushinwa buteganyijwe kugira igipimo cyo kutagira ibimenyetso kiri hasi gato kuri 44%.
Igihe cyo kubaho (igihe hagati yo kwandura no gutangira kugaragaza ibimenyetso) ni iminsi 1 kugeza ku 14; ibisanzwe ni iminsi itanu. Nk'urugero rw'ibipimo bidashidikanywaho, imibare y'abantu bafite COVID-19 batakaje ibyiyumvo byo guhumurirwa yabanje kuba 30% hanyuma iragabanuka igera kuri 15%.
Hari ibindi bisobanuro by'uburyo iyi ndwara ishobora kwaduka bitaramenyekana.
Bivugwa ko iyi ndwara yibonekeza cyane cyane mu gihe cyo guhura no guhura n'abantu bake cyane mu gihe cyo gukoresha ibiyobyabwenge bya kokayine, pidgin cyangwa kuvuga; guhura cyane bishobora kuba hagati ya metero 1 na 2 (3 na 6 ft).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko cocaine yasutswe mu mubiri ituma ibinyabuzima bigera ku metero 4.5 (15 ft) kugeza kuri metero 8.2 (27 ft).
Bamwe bagaragaje ko virusi ishobora kwandura binyuze mu matembabuzi mato cyane amara igihe kirekire mu mwuka, ashobora guterwa no kuvuga. Amatara yo mu mwuka ashobora guterwa no guhumeka, harimo no kuvuga, nubwo virusi idashobora kwandura mu mwuka.
Amataratara ashobora guterwa mu kanwa cyangwa mu kanwa k'abantu ba hafi cyangwa akishyirwa mu bihaha.
Hari uburyo bwo kuvura nk'imashini zo kuvura mu myanya y'ubuhumekero (CPR) zishobora gutuma umwanda w'ibihaha ujya mu mwuka, bityo bigatuma umwuka usakara.
Bishobora no gukwirakwira iyo umuntu akoze ku kintu cyanduye, nko ku ruhu, maze agakora ku maso, ku munwa cyangwa ku marira.
Nubwo hari impungenge ko ishobora gukwirakwira mu myanda, iki kibazo cyitezwe ko ari gito.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yahakanye ko nta buryo bwo kwanduzanya binyuze mu myenda y'umunwa bwa SARS-CoV2. Virusi ikwirakwira cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, nubwo bishobora kuba byarabaye mbere yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso no mu byiciro byakurikiyeho by'indwara.
Abantu bagaragayeho ubwandu bwa virusi itera SIDA mbere y'iminsi itatu batangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko ubwandu bushobora kubaho mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara.
Hari raporo nke gusa z'abanduye-bakekwaho indwara zidakorwaho ibimenyetso, ariko ubwandu butarakorwaho ibimenyetso bwemejwe n'ibihugu byinshi mu gihe cy'iperereza ry'ibikurikiraho.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurwanya Indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo bitamenyekanye neza uko iyi ndwara yandura, umuntu umwe ashobora kwandura abantu babiri cyangwa batatu.
By'umwihariko, virusi yagaragaye ku bicuruzwa bya plastiki (polypropylene) n'ibyuma 304, ku munsi umwe ku mbuga za interineti, no ku minsi ine ku muringa.
Icyakora, ibi biterwa n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe. Amatungo n'ibindi bikoko bishobora kuba byanduye COVID-19.
Nta gihamya igaragaza ko inyamaswa zishobora kwanduza abantu, nubwo abategetsi bo mu Bwongereza batanga inama yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukora ku nyamaswa, nko nyuma yo guhura n'imyenda abantu banduye bashobora kuba barakozeho.
Virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ni virusi nshya, yabanje gutandukanywa n'abantu batatu barwaye indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha mu gihe cy'icyiciro cy'abarwaye indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha i Wuhan.
Ibintu byose biranga SARS-CoV-2 biranga coronavirus. Hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, virusi yica isabune yo mu rugo, ikangiza uruhu rw'umurinzi. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya hafi na SARS-CoV y'umwimerere.
Bemeza ko ari inyamaswa.
Isesengura rusange ryagaragaje ko coronavirus ifitanye isano mu buryo bw'imiterere na genome ya Beccovirus, mu bwoko bw'ibinyabuzima by'ibanze bya Sarcovirus (umurongo B) hamwe na sitireni ebyiri zafashwe mu birura.
Ni 96% bisa n'ibisanzwe ku zindi ndwara za Coronavirus z'ingore (BatCov TaTG13).
Muri Gashyantare 2020, abashakashatsi bo mu Bushinwa bemeje ko hari itandukaniro rimwe gusa rya amino acide mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'urukurikirane rwa genome hagati ya virusi zo mu bwoko bwa pangolin n'iz'abantu.
Kugeza ubu, kugereranya kwa genome byose byageze kuri 92% by'ibintu rusange byo mu rwego rwa jenome hagati ya coronavirus ya pangolin na SARS-CoV-2, ibyo bikaba bidahagije kugira ngo hagaragazwe ko pangolin ari yo yari ikorera mu cyumba cy'indembe.
Kwibasirwa na virusi birashobora gukorwa hashingiwe ku bimenyetso, nubwo byemezwa byanze bikunze binyuze mu gusubiza inyuma imikorere ya serivisi ya polimeri (rRT-PCR) y'umusemburo wanduye cyangwa imirasire ya CT.
Ubushakashatsi bugereranyije PCR na CT mu mujyi wa Wuhan bwagaragaje ko CT ifite ubushobozi bwo kumva neza kurusha PCR, nubwo idasobanutse neza, ifite umwihariko wo kurasa cyane mu bindi bikorwa by'ubuhumekero n'izindi ndwara.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika cy'Ubuvuzi bw'Imiterere cyatangaje ko "CT itagomba gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa nk'icyiciro cya mbere cyo gupima COVID-19".
OMS yasohoye amabwiriza menshi yo gupima RNA ya SARS-CoV-2, iyambere yasohotse ku ya 17 Mutarama.
Iki cyemezo gikoresha uburyo bwo gusubiza mu buryo bw'uruvange bwa polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR).
Ibizamini bishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'umwuka cyangwa amaraso.
Ibisubizo bikunze kugaragara nyuma y'amasaha make kugeza ku minsi mike.
Ubusanzwe iki kizamini gikorwa ku isamu y'umuhogo-umwotsi nubwo isamu y'umuhogo ishobora gukoreshwa. Ibitaro byinshi n'amasosiyete biri gukora ibizamini bya serolojiya, byerekana antibodies.
Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, nta na kimwe muri ibi cyemejwe ko gihagije kugira ngo cyemerewe gukoreshwa mu buryo bwagutse.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, ibizamini bya seroloji byakozwe na Cellex kandi byemejwe gukoreshwa byihuse gusa na za laboratwari zizwi.
Ibimenyetso by'ubushakashatsi bwihariye kuri radiyo na tomography ya mudasobwa (CT) by'abantu bafite ibimenyetso birimo urumuri rwinshi rw'ibirahuri byo hasi kandi nta kwisiga kw'impande.
Umuryango w'ubushakashatsi mu by'imashini zo mu Butaliyani ushyira hamwe amakuru yo kuri interineti agaragaza ibisubizo by'imashini z'imashini zo mu bwoko bwa radiyo zemeza ko umuntu afite iyo ndwara.
Kubera ubwandu bw'izindi ndwara nka Adenovirus, iradiyasi idashobora kwemezwa na PCR ifite ubushobozi buke bwo gupima COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye bwakozwe mu Bushinwa bwagereranyije ibisubizo bya CT na PCR kandi bwerekana ko nubwo iradiyo idasobanura cyane ubwandu, ariko ko yihuta kandi ko ifite ubushobozi bwo kumenya, byerekana ko ishobora gufatwa nk'ikoresho cyo gupima mu turere turimo icyorezo.
Urubuga rwa neurone rw'uruhu rushingiye ku bwenge bw'ikoranabuhanga rwatangijwe kugirango hamenyekane ibintu byerekana iradiyo hamwe na radiographie na CT.
Uburyo bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara burimo kwirinda isuku, gukaraba intoki, kwirinda gukaraba amaso, izuru cyangwa umunwa n'intoki zitahanaguwe, gukoresha cocaine cyangwa pidgmine mu myenda no kujugunya mu myanda imyanda.
Abarwayi bagirwa inama yo kwambara udupfukamunwa mu ruhame.
Ingamba zo kwirinda abantu ku buryo bw'umubiri na zo zirasabwa mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo. Guverinoma nyinshi zashyizeho amategeko yo kugabanya cyangwa gutanga inama ku ngendo zose zidakenewe no kwirinda ibihugu cyangwa uturere twanduye.
Icyakora, virusi yageze ku cyiciro cyo gukwirakwira mu baturage mu bice by'isi bikennye.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi ikwirakwira mu baturage, kandi bamwe mu baturage ntibazi aho yavuye cyangwa uko yandura. Abatanga serivisi z'ubuzima bita ku muntu ushobora kuba yanduye basabwe kubanza kumenya ibipimo by'ubwirinzi no kwirinda guhura n'abantu no gukoresha ubwirinzi bw'amaso. Gukurikirana guhura n'abantu ni uburyo bw'ingenzi ku bayobozi b'ubuzima bwo kumenya inkomoko y'indwara no kwirinda ko yandura.
Gukoresha amakuru yerekeye aho umuntu ari kuri telefoni zigendanwa na guverinoma kuri iyi mpamvu byateje impungenge ku byerekeye ubuzima bwite, hamwe na Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 atanga ibisobanuro asaba ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ubu buryo bwo kugenzura.
Porogaramu nyinshi za terefone zashyizwe mu bikorwa cyangwa zasabwe gukoresha ku bushake, kandi kugeza ku itariki ya 7 Werurwe 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi na abiri y'abahanga yakoraga ku bisubizo by'ibikoresho by'ibanze, nk'ikoreshwa rya Bluetooth mu kwandika hafi umukoresha kuri terefone zindi.
Abakoresha nyuma bahabwa ubutumwa niba bari mu biganiro bya bugufi n'umuntu wagaragayeho COVID-19.Ibitekerezo bitari byo byakwirakwijwe ku buryo bwo kwirinda kwandura; kurinda amazuru, nk'akarorero, no gukaraba mu kanwa n'umwandazi w'umunwa ntacyo bimaze.
Nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 ruriho, nubwo bishobora kuba biri gukorwa n'imiryango.
Gukaraba intoki birasabwa mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
CDC itera abantu inkunga yo gukaraba intoki mbere y'igihe bakoresheje isabune n'amazi nibura mu gihe cy'amasegonda 20, cyane cyane nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero cyangwa igihe intoki zabo zanduye cyane; mbere yo kurya; no nyuma yo gukaraba umunwa, gukoresha cocaine cyangwa pidgin.
Ibi biterwa nuko hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, virusi yica isabune yo mu rugo, ikangiza ingufu zayo.
CDC ikomeza itera inkunga gukoresha umuti wica imibu ufite nibura 60% by'imibu iyo isabune n'amazi bitaraboneka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) risaba abantu kwirinda gukorakora amaso, amazuru, cyangwa umunwa batabanje gukaraba intoki.
Ibikoresho bishobora guhanagurwa mu buryo bwinshi (mu munota umwe uhereye igihe cy'imikorere y'ibikoresho byo gusukura ibyuma), harimo 62-71% ya éthanol, 50-100% ya isopropanol, 0.1% ya sodium hydrochloride, 0.5% ya hydroxyde d'hydrogène na 0.2-7.5% ya iodine-povioidine.
Ibindi binure, nka benzalkonium chloride na gluconate ya crohexidine, ntabwo bikora cyane.
CDC irasaba ko mu gihe umuntu akekwaho cyangwa yemeza ko yanduye COVID-19 mu kigo nk'icyumba cy'ubuvuzi cyangwa mu bitaro, ahantu hose nko mu biro, mu bwiherero, ahantu hahurira abantu benshi, ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki abantu bakoresha nk'utubanda, utwuma two kwerekaho ibintu, utubati, konti, udukoresho two kugenzura kure, na ATM zikoreshwa n'umuntu urwaye, bigomba guhanagurwa virusi.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuzima atanga inama yo gutwikira umunwa n'umunwa n'ibikoresho byo mu kanwa mu gihe umuntu arimo kunywa cocaine cyangwa pidgin, no guhita atakaza ibyo bikoresho.
Kwambara agapfukamunwa ni ingenzi ku bantu bashobora kuba baranduye iyi virusi, kuko kwambara agapfukamunwa bigabanya ingano n'aho udutotsi two mu mwuka duturuka mu gihe umuntu avuga, ahema cyangwa yitsamura.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatanze amabwiriza y'igihe n'uburyo bwo kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Nk'uko bivugwa na Stephen Griffin, umuhanga mu by'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa virusi wo muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, "kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu batakaza mu maso, ari na yo soko y'ingenzi y'indwara z'ibibembe".
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, nk'abita ku muntu urwaye COVID-19, nubwo ryemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda guhura n'ikibazo cyo kubura mu maso.
Ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gushishikariza abaturage kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, CDC irasaba kwambara udupfukamunwa tudafite ubumara dukorwa mu myenda. Ubushinwa bwifuza cyane gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi dukoreshwa rimwe na rimwe n'abaturage bafite ubuzima bwiza, cyane cyane mu gihe bahuye na hafi (metero 1 (ibirenge 3) cyangwa munsi) n'abandi bantu.
Hong Kong irasaba kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe ukoresha imodoka cyangwa mu gihe uri ahantu hari abantu benshi.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Thailand batera abantu inkunga yo gukora udupfukamunwa tw'impu mu ngo zabo no kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza kubanza gukaraba buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Tchèque na Slovakia bibuza abantu kujya hanze y'igihugu batambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa udupfukamunwa.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame kugira ngo birinde ndetse barinde n'abandi.
Leta ya Autriche yategetse ko umuntu wese ugiye guhaha agomba kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Israel yasabye abaturage bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame.
Taiwan, imaze gukora udupfukamunwa tugera kuri miliyoni icumi buri munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, yasabye abagenzi bo mu mihanda ya gari ya moshi na bisi kwambara udupfukamunwa guhera ku ya 1 Mata.
Panama yasabye abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa igihe bari hanze, mu gihe yasabye ko abantu badashobora kugura udupfukamunwa bakorera udupfukamunwa mu ngo zabo.
Mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore, ibigo byinshi by'ubucuruzi bikoresha udupfukamunwa.
Kwitarura abandi (nanone bita Ferian distancing) ni ibikorwa byo kurwanya indwara bigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya guhura cyane kw'abantu.
Imihanda irimo kuba mu kato, ingendo zihagaritswe; ndetse n'ibigo by'amashuri, ibibanza by'amateka, ibibuga by'imikino, za sitade cyangwa ibigo by'ubucuruzi bifunze.
Abantu bashobora gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwitandukanya n'abandi mu kuguma mu rugo, kugabanya ingendo, kwirinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, gukoresha indamutso zitemewe, no kwitandukanya n'abandi.
Ubu leta nyinshi zisaba cyangwa ziteganya ko abantu batandukanywa n'abandi mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Umubare munini w'amateraniro wagabanyijwe n'inzego za leta ya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima kuva ku bantu 250 (niba nta COVID-19 izwi muri ako karere) ukagera ku bantu 50, hanyuma ukagera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwashyizeho itegeko ribuza abantu benshi guteranira hamwe mu bantu babiri. Abakuze n'abafite ibibazo by'ubuzima nk'indwara ya diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso n'ibibazo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri, bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye kandi CDC yabasabye kuguma mu rugo igihe cyose bishoboka aho icyorezo cy'abaturage cyabaye. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima zatangiye guhindura uburyo bwo gukoresha "kwirinda" ku "kureka" "kureka", gusobanura ko intego ari ugugabanya guhura mu buryo bw'umubiri mu gihe cyo guhura n'abantu, haba mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo cyangwa kure.
Gukoresha igitekerezo cyo "gutandukanya abantu" byatumye abantu bagomba kwitabira kwitandukanya n'abandi, aho kubatera inkunga yo kuguma mu bandi ku mpamvu zinyuranye.
Ibi bikubiyemo inama yo gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina gusa n'umuntu ubana na we, udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Kwishyira mu kato mu rugo byasabwe ku bantu bafite COVID-19 n'abakekwaho kuyandura.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza y'ubufatanye ku bwigenge bukwiye. Guverinoma nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye ko abaturage bose baba mu duce twatewe n'icyorezo bose bishyira mu kato.
Amabwiriza akomeye cyane yo kwisanzura yashyizweho ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 kandi bakaba baherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere karimo ubwandu bw'icyorezo, basabwe kwiherera mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 uhereye igihe baherukaga guhuriraho.
Uburyo bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo ni uguhagarika cyangwa kugabanya, no kugabanya.
Gukumira indwara mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo bigamije gutahura no gutandukanya ubwandu hamwe no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kugenzura indwara n'inkingo zo guhagarika icyorezo ngo kidakwirakwira mu baturage.
Iyo nta buryo bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo bubonetse, imbaraga zitangira kujya mu byiciro byo kugabanya: ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo no kugabanya ingaruka ku mashyirahamwe y'ubuzima n'abaturage.
Ingamba zo kugabanya no kugabanya ingano z'ibinyampeke zishobora guterwa icyarimwe.
Kwirinda bisaba ingamba nyinshi, mu rwego rwo guhindura ikwirakwira ry'indwara kuva ku muntu umwe ujya ku wundi mu rwego rwo kugabanya kimwe mu bice byo kugenzura no guhangana n'ikwirakwira ry'indwara y'ibicurane, kugerageza kugabanya icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane bishobora kuvugwa nko gukosora igiciro cy'ikwirakwira.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo gutakaza serivisi kandi bigatanga igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ingamba zitari iz'ubuvuzi zishobora kugenzura icyorezo zirimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko gusukura intoki, kwambara agapfukamunwa, no kwigunga; ingamba z'abaturage zigamije gutandukanya abantu n'abandi, nko gufunga amashuri no kwanga amateraniro manini; uruhare rw'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibyo bikorwa; hamwe n'ingamba z'ibidukikije, nko gusukura udupfukamunwa. Ingamba z'ingenzi cyane zigamije kugabanya icyorezo mu Bushinwa zagiye zirushaho kwiyongera igihe icyorezo cyagaragaye, nko gushyira mu kato imigi yose no gushyiraho amategeko akomeye yo kugenzura ingendo.
Ibihugu byinshi byashyizeho ingamba zo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho igerageza rusange n'igenzurwa ry'abantu mu ngo, kandi itanga umuburo ku miterere y'abantu banduye.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku banduye biyemeje kwihererana kandi ishyiraho ibihano bikaze ku batabikurikiza.
Taiwan yongereye umusaruro w'udupfukamunwa kandi ihana abantu benshi bagura ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ibyo ni na ko bimeze ku Bwongereza na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, bigaragaza ko kugabanya (guhagarika aho guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) no kugabanya (guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo) ari imbogamizi zikomeye.
Gucika neza bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abasaba ubuvuzi ku kigero cya 2/3 n'urupfu ku kigero cya kimwe cya kabiri, ariko biracyatuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa kandi bigatuma ubuzima bw'abantu buhagaze nabi.
Gucukura bishobora kwemerwa ariko bigomba kurindwa kugeza igihe virusi ikwirakwijwe mu baturage (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo rubonetse, niba ari ubwa mbere), kuko ikwirakwira rishobora kwiyongera mugihe ingamba zirangiye.
Gushyiraho ingamba ndende zo guhashya icyorezo bizagira ingaruka ku mibereho myiza y'abaturage n'ubukungu.
Nta muti wihariye wa virusi wa COVID-19, ariko hagiye hakorwa ingamba zo kuwushyira mu bikorwa, harimo no kugerageza imiti ikoreshwa ubu.
Kunywa imiti igabanya ubukana, kunywa amazi menshi, no kuruhuka bishobora gufasha mu kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere bwayo, imiti ya ogisijeni, uruvange rw'amaraso, n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka bishobora kuba ngombwa.
Gukoresha imiti ikangura bishobora gutuma ibisubizo birushaho kuba bibi.
Ibice byinshi byemewe mbere byo kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi biri gukorwaho ubushakashatsi kugira ngo bikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko hari "uburyo bwo kuvura budahangarwa kandi budahangarwa" bushobora kugabanya ibimenyetso bya SARS-CoV-19.
Kwongera ubushobozi no kugera ku buvuzi ku bakomeretse ba COVID-19 byasobanuwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) nk'uburyo bwo guhashya icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere by'u Burayi bya OMS byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze kugira ngo bahindure ibikoresho ku byiciro bitandukanye, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu bikorwa byo gupima COVID-19, guhitamo uburyo bwo gupima igihe cyose bibaye ngombwa, gushyira mu kato abarwayi bafite COVID-19, no kuzamura ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi cyane binyuze mu guhugura abakozi no kongera umubare w'imashini z'ubuhumekero n'ibitanda biboneka.
Hari ibitekerezo byinshi ku byerekeye aho indwara ya mbere (yitwa indwara y'umubare wa zeru) yakomotse.
Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba yarabayeho tariki ya 1 Mutarama 2019 i Wuhan, Hubei, Ubushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wiyongereye cyane.
Benshi muri bo bari bafitanye isano n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huang, ryagurishwagaho n'amatungo mazima, kandi igitekerezo kimwe ni uko virusi yavuye muri kimwe muri ibyo biremwa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ko ifite inkomoko y'inyamaswa. Impamvu idasobanutse y'indwara y'ibihaha yagaragaye ku ya 26 Ukuboza, kandi ivurwa na Dr. Zhang Jixuan wo mu bitaro by'intara ya Hubei, waburiye CDC ya Jinghan mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ku "coronavirus isa na SARS".
Abaganga umunani, barimo Li Wenliang, bari barahawe imiburo n'abapolisi ko bakwirakwizaga poropagande y'ibinyoma, undi witwa Ifen, yari yarashyizweho n'abakozi be bakuru kubera ko yari yarakomeje gukangurira abantu kwirinda.
Nyuma yaho, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan yatangaje itangazo ryo ku wa 31 Ukuboza, kandi itangazwa na OMS.
Ibibazo bikomeye by'indwara y'ibihaha itera indwara zitazwi byatangajwe n'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bw'i Wuhan mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu byiciro bya mbere by'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu tundi duce tw'Ubushinwa, ifashijwe n'impunzi z'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa ndetse na Wuhan, ikigo cy'ingendo n'imihanda ya gari ya moshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwongeye gutangaza abandi bantu 140 bashya banduye, barimo babiri i Beijing n'undi umwe i Shenzhen.
Nyuma, amakuru yemewe yerekana ko kugeza ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, abantu bagera ku 6174 bagaragaje ibimenyetso. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yarushije Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani umubare munini w'abanduye kw'isi. Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abantu barenga miliyoni 1.61 baranduye ku isi, abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye, abarenga 364,000 barakize.
Mu bihugu bigera kuri 200 n'uturere dufite nibura umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu kandi bishyiraho imipaka.
Ibisubizo byigihugu byaranzwe n'ingamba zirimo kwishyirira mu kato (nk'amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo, amabwiriza yo kwihisha, cyangwa kwirinda kwivana mu rugo) no kubuza abantu kwinjira mu ngo. Ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, hafi 90% by'abatuye isi, bari mu buryo bwo kuguma mu rugo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu rugo muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo bari mu rugo, na miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde bari mu rugo.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu buryo runaka bwo kuguma mu rugo, buzamuka bujya kuri miliyari 2.6 mu minsi ibiri yakurikiyeho - hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 ni uwa Wuhan ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; raporo imwe itari yemejwe igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye ari uwa 17 Ukuboza.
Dr Zhang Jixun yabonye ko hari umuntu wari urwaye indwara y'ibihaha ku itariki ya 26 Mutarama, bituma ibitaro bye bimenyesha CDC ya Wuhan ku itariki ya 27 Mutarama.
Isuzuma ry'ibanze ry'ibinyabuzima ryakozwe ku murwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 ryemeje ko coronavirus isa na SARS.
Itangazo rusange ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza.
Umuryango Mpuzamahanga wita ku Buzima (OMS) wabimenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Mu gihe izo ngamba zafashwe, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bari barahawe umuburo n'igipolisi ko "bafite amakuru menshi" ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'ubuzima y'igihugu y'Ubushinwa yabanje gutangaza ko nta "gihamya igaragara" y'ubwandu bw'abantu ku bantu.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatangiye ubukangurambaga bukaze bwaje kuvugwa n'Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka rya Kominisiti ry'Ubushinwa nk'"intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Mu cyiswe "igikorwa cy'igenzura cya mbere mu mateka y'abantu", ku ya 23 Mutarama, hatangajwe itegeko ryo guhagarika ingendo zijya no ziva muri Wuhan, ryongerewe mu mijyi 15 yo muri Hubei, rigira ingaruka ku bantu miliyoni 57.
Imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo zarabujijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (ku ya 25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe mu duce twinshi.
Abategetsi kandi batangaje ko kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Husein Shan, byarangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hari ikindi bitaro byubatswe, ibitaro bya Licheshan, kugira ngo bikomeze kuvura izindi ndwara.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 i Wuhan, nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro na stade, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, guverinoma yongeye gufata ingamba zo kwirinda COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku bakerarugendo no kongera ikiruhuko cya Spring Festival.
Kaminuza n'amashuri na byo byafunzwe mu gihugu hose.
Intara ya Hong Kong na Macao zashyizeho ingamba nyinshi, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuli makuru.
Ingamba zo gukorera kure zashyizweho mu bice byinshi by'Ubushinwa.
Ingendo ku bantu baturuka mu gihugu cya Hubei n'abaturuka muri icyo gihugu zashyizweho.
Imodoka zitwara abantu n'ibintu by'abantu bose zarasenyutse, kandi amazu ndangamurage yo hirya no hino mu Bushinwa yarafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Gucunga uburyo bwo gutwara abantu mu mujyi byashyizwe mu bikorwa mu mijyi myinshi, kandi byitezwe ko abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abatuye isi) bazaba bari mu buryo runaka bwo guhagarika ingendo. Nyuma y'aho icyorezo cyerekeje ku isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo gukumira "kuzana" virusi mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo kwisanzura ku bakerarugendo bose b'amahanga binjira mu mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa hari umuntu umwe gusa wari waranduye mu gihugu mu minsi itanu, muri iki gihe akaba yari umuturage wari uturutse i Guangzhou mu mujyi wa Istanbul.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa Li Keqiang yatangaje ko icyorezo cy'ubwandu bw'ibanze mu gihugu cyahagaritswe kandi ko icyorezo cyagenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingendo ku bantu bo mu ntara ya Hubei, uretse i Wuhan, zaragabanyijwe nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo kuguma mu rugo. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa byo gutura bizasubikwa kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta bisobanuro by'igihe politiki izarangirira.
Abashaka kujya mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba Visa muri Ambasade cyangwa muri Konsula z'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi gufungura ibikorwa byayo ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku masosiyete. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kwibuka utangira n'umunsi w'umwiherero w'iminota itatu saa 10:00 z'ijoro ku ya 4 Mata, bihuriye n'umunsi mukuru wa Qingming, nubwo guverinoma nkuru yasabye imiryango gukomeza kwitandukanya n'abandi kugira ngo irinde ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri Koreya y'Epfo cyemejwe ko cyaturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 20 Gashyantare, ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko habayeho kuzamuka gukomeye, ahanini biturutse ku iteraniro ry'idini ry'i Daegu rizwi nka Shinsengumi Church of Christ.
Abaturage bo mu gace ka Shincheongji bari baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan basuye umujyi wa Daegu bakekwaho kuba ari bo bateje iki cyorezo.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9336 b'iryo dini, 1,261 cyangwa hafi 13% bari bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020 ari bwo yabonye umubare munini w'abari mu bihe by'akaga.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, ku ya 29 Gashyantare bagera ku 3150.
Inzego zose z'igisirikare muri Koreya zashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko ibizamini byemeje ko abasirikare batatu banduye.
Ibi byagize ingaruka ku ngengabihe y'ingendo z'indege, bituma zitangira guhinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda ikomeye kandi nziza ku isi yo gupima abaturage virusi, no gushyira mu kato abantu bose banduye no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu banduye.
Uburyo bwo kwisuzumisha bwagombaga kuba bugizwe no gutanga raporo ku buryo bw'agateganyo ku bantu bavuye mu bindi bihugu bageze muri icyo gihugu bakoresheje porogaramu ya telefoni, gupima virusi mu modoka iyo umusaruro uboneka ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 20,000 ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo ifatwa nk'aho ari intsinzi mu kurwanya icyorezo nubwo nta mujyi wose uri mu kato. Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo wari waratangiye kwicamo ibice ku buryo Perezida Moon In-Jie yabyitabiriye.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku birego basaba ko Moon ashinjwa kuba yarateye utwatsi uburyo leta ikora, cyangwa se bashima uko yitwaye.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi umwe mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, ingendo zose z'abanyamahanga zizashyirwa mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ibinyamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yabonye ubufasha bwo gupima virusi buvuye mu bihugu 121.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Irani yatangaje umuntu wa mbere wemejweho SARS-CoV-2 muri Qum, aho nyuma yaho uwo munsi abantu babiri bapfuye, nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi yabitangaje.
Ingamba z'ibanze zatangajwe na leta zirimo kubuza ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, ibirori bya siporo, amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga za kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri yisumbuye n'amashuri.
Iran yatanze miliyari 5 z'amanyarwanda mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato abantu bose bagaragaye ko banduye, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bagomba gushyirwa mu kato.
Mu kwezi kwa Werurwe, hatangajwe gahunda yo kugabanya urujya n'uruza hagati y'imijyi, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwinshi hagati y'imijyi rwatangiye mbere y'umwaka mushya wa Nourruz.
Kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, imva z'aba Shiite z'i Qum' zigumye zifunguye ku bayoboke.
Mu gihe hari abiyita ko bahisha ko iki cyorezo cyadutse muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byasubije abanduye muri Irani ku ya 28 Gashyantare, byerekana ko iki cyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye cyane kuruta 388 leta ya Irani yatangaje icyo gihe.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, 23 muri 290 bayifite bayandura ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura by'agateganyo abaharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira gukora ibikorwa by'amahoro, ndetse no kurekura by'agateganyo abandi bafungwa bose bakwiriye.
Yavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwira virusi mu bigo bifunze, nk'ibigo by'ubudehe, aho kwitabwaho n'abaganga bidakenewe.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, umubare munini w'abapfuye mu munsi umwe mu gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Nibura abanyapolitiki 12 ba Irani n'abayobozi ba leta bapfuye bazize iki cyorezo kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite ubwandu bushya bwa coronavirus buri saha 50 n'urupfu rumwe buri minota 10.
Nk'uko bivugwa n'umuyobozi wa OMS, umubare w'abanduye ushobora kuba ukubye incuro eshanu uwo muri Irani.
Byemejwe kandi ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bizagira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu bwo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Komiseri Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ku Burenganzira bw'Ikiremwamuntu yasabye ko ibihugu byazahajwe n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani, byongererwa ingufu mu bukungu.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, icyorezo cyemejwe mu Butaliyani, ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bari i Roma bagaragaye ko banduye SARS-CoV-2.
Ibibazo byazamutse cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege ziva cyangwa zijya mu Bushinwa kandi itangaza ibihe bidasanzwe.
Nyuma yaho, havumbuwe itsinda ry'abantu batanduye COVID-19, hamwe n'abantu 16 bemejwe ko banduye i Lombardy, guhera ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatanze itegeko rishya ryo gukumira icyorezo, nko gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 mu turere 11 dutandukanye two mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe, Giuseppe Conte, yagize ati "Mu bice by'icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka ntibishobora gutangwa.
Gufunga ibikorwa by'akazi n'imyidagaduro byategetswe muri utwo turere. "Ku ya 4 Werurwe, guverinoma y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza zose zifunga burundu kubera ko Ubutaliyani bwageze ku 100".
Ibikorwa byose by'imikino ikomeye, harimo imikino y'umupira w'amaguru ya Serie A, bizakorwa nta nkomyi kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe burundu nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bihagarikwa uretse supermarket n'amaduka y'imiti. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Gukumira, Gucubya, Gucunga no Kurinda (SIAARTI) cyatanze inama ku bijyanye n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye n'amabwiriza y'ibanze ashobora gukurikizwa.
