Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yongeye gutangira ku wa 3 Werurwe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati, amashuri yose yo mu gihugu yose yarafunzwe. Ku wa 6 Werurwe 2020, Amerika yasabye ko hagaragazwa ingaruka za coronavirus nshya ku gihugu n'itsinda ry'inzobere mu by'indwara zo mu Bwongereza muri Imperial College London.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo gukuraho ibikoresho by'ubwiteganyirize bwa coronavirus no gusubiza, ryatanze miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari y'ingoboka ku bigo bya leta kugira ngo bikemure iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubucuruzi yahagaritse ingendo z'abakozi, avanaho inama, kandi atera abakozi inkunga yo gukorera mu rugo.
Ibikorwa n'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko ingendo zihagaritswe mu Burayi bwose, usibye Ubwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, yagutse kugabanya umubare w'abimukira mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu, ashyiraho amafaranga ya leta kugira ngo ahangane n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi bwafunzwe cyangwa buhagarika amasaha y'akazi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika mu rwego rwo guhashya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu bihugu byose 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko New York City yari ifite abantu 10,700 banduye coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, Hakeem yavuze ko kuba abantu barigendera kure byagaragaye ko ari ingirakamaro, kuko byitezwe ko kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abanduye bigabanuka kuva ku minsi 2.0 kugeza ku minsi 4.7.
