Nk'uko byavuzwe n'ibitangazamakuru ku ya 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwitandukanya n'abandi kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, UNSS Comfort, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1000, bwageze i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Amerika yatangaje ko abantu 884 bishwe na coronavirus mu masaha 24 gusa.
Ku ya 3 Mata, ubwandu bwageze ku 100,000 muri Leta ya New York. Ibiro bya White House byanenzwe kutagira icyo bitanga ku kaga no kugenzura itangazamakuru binyuze mu kuyobora abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi gufatanya gusobanura no gutanga amakuru rusange ajyanye na virusi n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Muri rusange, kwemera ko Trump ari we ugiye gufata icyemezo cy'uko iki cyorezo kizahagarara, byaciwemo ibice n'amashyaka atandukanye.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika n'abashakashatsi banenze ko Amerika ikeneye cyane ibicuruzwa by'ingenzi, nk'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ubuvuzi biva mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'uburyo bwo gutwara abantu hakoreshejwe umwuka ryakoreshejwe mu kumenya no guhanura uburyo bw'ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo kandi ryatangajwe mu kinyamakuru cya Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa Nzeri 2020.
Nk'uko byemejwe n'ibiro by'ingendo z'indege ku isi (International Air Transport Association) mu 2018, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, na Taipei ni byo bifite umubare munini w'abagenzi bavuye i Wuhan.
