Air New Zealand Transport yageze i Auckland ku ya 5/2; abagenzi bayo (bamwe bari abo muri Australia na Pacifique) bari bari mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Hangoveru mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
