Ibisubizo by'ibizamini byemeje ko abaturage bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi ba za ndege, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare, bari mu bikorwa bya gisirikare. Mu rwego rwo gukemura ibibazo, bose bagumye bagenzurwa kandi ntibagirwa mu kato iminsi 14 muri Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Umuryango w'Abibumbye watangiye gutandukanya ingabo zawo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5/2, Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga wa Sin yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (birimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byohereje imfashanyo muri Sin.
Abanyeshuri bamwe na bamwe bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bashyize hamwe kugira ngo boherereze imfashanyo mu turere twanduye, hamwe n'itsinda rinini ry'akarere ka Chicago rihuriweho na Raporo ryayoboye kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa N95 ku bitaro byo mu karere ka Hubei ku ya 30/1 . Umuryango w'abagiraneza wo kohereza imfashanyo, Relief Circle, ku bufatanye na FedEx, wohereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'abantu, birimo utwenda tw'amaboko n'imyenda, byatumijwe n'indege yihutirwa ku bitaro bya Wan Onin ku ya 30/1.
Ku itariki ya 5/2, umuryango wa Bill na Melinda Gates watangaje ko ugiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika ku muntu uzashakisha umuti wo gukingira "abantu bafite ibyago byinshi muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo".
Interaction yatangaje ko guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 ku baturage ba Filipine muri Mata, nyuma y'aho Centra Richard Gordon igeze muri Wuhan ifite udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapuru yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari y'Amerika muri Sine.
U Buyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu mujyi wa Wan. Malaysia yatangaje ko yatanze toni 18 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Sin. Ubudage bwohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bya virusi birimo udupfukamunwa 10,000 twa virusi.
Muri Werurwe, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ubufasha bw'ubuvuzi n'inzobere mu Butaliyani mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo muri icyo gihugu.
Bwana May wo mu bucuruzi yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1 by'imiti, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyambaro 60,000 yo kurinda abantu i Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, kugira ngo bihabwe Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho 5,000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 na za ventilators 5 muri Panama.
Ibihugu bya Holande, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Tchèque byatanze ibitekerezo byabo ku bipimo bya masike n'ibikoresho by'ibipimo bya Sin.
