Ububiligi bwasubije mu gihugu ibipfukamunwa 100,000 bitakoreshejwe, byitezwe ko byakozwe muri Sin, ariko mu by'ukuri byakozwe muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga ya Sine yakiriwe neza mu bice bya Amerika y'Epfo na Aziya muri 4/2. Banki y'Isi yatangiye kohereza inkunga yihuse mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) rishimye cyane ibikorwa by'u Bushinwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyadutse hagati ya 2002-2004. Leta y'u Bushinwa ishinjwa kudahishira virusi, bituma imihati yo gukumira no kurandura virusi idahera, kandi muri iki gihe, leta y'ibanze "yatanga icyegeranyo cyemewe n'amategeko cyo kwirinda icyorezo mu biruhuko by'umugi wa New York".
Ku ya 23/1 , mu rwego rwo kwitabira icyemezo cya guverinoma nkuru cyo guhagarika urujya n'uruza mu mujyi wa Wan, umuyobozi wa OMS Gaudin Galia yatangaje ko nubwo "ntabyumvikane neza ko ari itegeko rya OMS" byari ikimenyetso gikomeye cyo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu karere aho virusi yari ikomeye cyane. Byatangajwe ko "nta kindi cyigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30/1 hashingiwe ku kwiyongera kw'ikwirakwira rya virusi kuva ku muntu umwe kugera ku wundi hanze ya China no kwiyongera kw'umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko gutangaza ibyago by'uburwayi bw'igihugu byatewe n'ubwoba bw'uko icyorezo kizasakara ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bikennye n'ibikennye bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza.
Mu gusubiza ku itegeko ryo guhagarika ingendo, Tedros yatangaje ko "nta mpamvu yo kugerageza kwivanga mu ngendo n'ubucuruzi ku isi" kandi ko "ubuyobozi bw'isi butazashyiraho amategeko agenga ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu rwego rwo kwitegura ibihugu bikennye, isaba Urukiko rwa Afurika gushyigikira ibihugu "bitagira uburyo bwo kwinjiza abantu banduye virusi, nubwo byaba biri mu bihe bikomeye".
Tedros yasobanuye ko "Iterambere ryacu riterwa n'imihati ya buri wese" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "gutanga uyu munsi cyangwa nyuma y'igihe runaka".Ku ya 11/2, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru COVID-19 nk'indwara.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres, yemeye gutanga "ingabo zose z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye mu bikorwa".
Umuyobozi w'itsinda ry'ibiza rya Loni yashyizwe mu bikorwa nk'ingaruka, bituma habaho ubufatanye bwa Loni bwose butuma OMS "yibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuzima mu gihe abandi bakozi bashobora kuzana ubunararibonye bwabo mu guhuza imibereho, ubukungu no guteza imbere ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo".
Ku ya 14/2, umuyobozi w'itsinda ry'ibikorwa by'ishyira mu bikorwa ry'igikorwa cy'ubuzima ku isi hamwe na WHO, yashyizwe mu bikorwa kugira ngo ahabwe impuguke mpuzamahanga n'ishami ry'ubuzima ku isi ku butaka bwa Sin kugira ngo bafashe gusuzuma no gucunga mu gihugu "imbaraga n'ubukana bw'icyorezo" bateguye amahugurwa no guhura n'ikigo cy'ibanze ku rwego rw'igihugu no gucunga ingendo z'abashyitsi mu karere kugira ngo bahitemo "ingaruka z'ibikorwa ku bantu batuye mu turere twitaruye n'ibindi bihugu, harimo n'ibiturage n'ibyaro". Ku ya 25/2, WHO yatangaje ko "isi igomba kurushaho kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus" ivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane kugira ngo ibihugu byitege icyorezo, "bigomba no kwitegura".
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo muri Irani, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatumye itsinda ry'abakozi muri Iran kugira ngo basuzume uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko ubwoba bw'icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi bwiyongera kuva ku "cyinshi" kugera ku "cyinshi cyane", aho cyagaragaye ko ari cyo cyiciro cyo hejuru cy'akaga n'imihangayiko".
McRyan, umuyobozi wa gahunda y'ibihe bidasanzwe ya OMS, mu kiganiro yahaye isi, yaburiye ko "hari ikigeragezo gikomeye ku butegetsi bwose ku isi: gukanguka.
Virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi ugomba kuba witeguye, "gushaka uburyo bukwiriye bwo kuyirwanya bishobora gufasha isi kwirinda ikiza cya virusi".
Ryan yatangaje ko amakuru ahari ubu atagaragaza impamvu zemewe z'ubuzima rusange zo gutangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko ari itangazo risobanura ko "twemera ko buri wese ku isi ashobora guhura n'iki cyorezo".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru yavuze ko OMS "ikomeje gukwirakwira ku kigero gikomeye kandi gikomeye, kandi ikomeje kugenda buhoro cyane" OMS ikomeza guhangana n'ikibazo gikomeye cy'icyorezo kitaraboneka, kirimo gutangaza vuba ibyihutirwa by'ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi mu byiciro by'icyorezo.
Impungenge z'abaturage zari zikubiyemo ikirego cy'umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, cyo gutanga imihoho, cyashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733,000 ku ya 6/4.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu b'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryashimangiye ko uburenganzira bw'abantu bose bwubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko abantu bose bafite ubuzima bwiza kandi ko leta ifite inshingano.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kubura amikoro cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba na rimwe kuba urwitwazo rwo kubarirwa mu matsinda.
Abahanga bemeje ko buri muntu afite uburenganzira bwo kugira ubuzima bwiza, harimo abafite ubumuga, amatsinda mato, abageze mu za bukuru, impunzi z'abatuye mu gihugu, abatagira aho baba, abari mu bukene, abantu bafunzwe, impunzi z'abimukira n'andi matsinda adakeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
