Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isuku y'amazi ni uburyo bwiza bwo guhangana n'ikibazo cyo kubura amazi n'isabune mu gihe cy'ingendo.
Amavuta y'inzoga akoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki agomba kuba arimo nibura 60% bya aluki.
Gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi byabaye itegeko nyuma y'aho umuganga w'Umunyahongiriya Ignaz Semmelweis avumbuye ingaruka zabyo (mu 1846) mu kwirinda indwara mu bitaro.
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bifasha abakozi b'ibitaro kwibuka gukaraba intoki iyo bibyibagiwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki byagabanyije ubwandu.
Gukaraba intoki byibuze mu gihe cy'amasegonda 15, ukoresheje isabune n'amazi cyangwa ikindi kintu cy'amazi kugira ngo uteremo umwuka kandi ukarabe intoki.
Intoki zigomba gukaraba mu buryo bwo gukomatanya no guhanagura.
Niba ufite umwanda munsi y'inkokora, hashobora gukoreshwa isutiye ifite ubugi.
Kubera ko mikorobe zishobora kuguma mu mazi yo ku ntoki, ni ngombwa ko uhanagura neza kandi ukayasukura neza.
Nyuma yo gukaraba, igikarabiro kigomba gukoreshwa mu kuvana amazi (cyangwa gufungura inzugi zose niba ari ngombwa)
Ibi birinda intoki kongera kwandura kubera ibyo bikoresho.
Gukaraba intoki ni ingenzi mu kwita ku buzima kugira ngo hatagira icyatera indwara.
Ikinyamakuru cy'ubuvuzi cya New England kivuga ko gukaraba intoki ku rugero ruto cyane bitemewe mu buzima bwa muganga, kandi ko abaganga benshi n'abaforomo bibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bityo bakandura mikorobe.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki neza n'ibindi bikorwa bishobora kugabanya ubwandu bw'udukoko mu maraso ku kigero cya 66%, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryatangaje inama y'uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki no kuzirinda.
Ubuyobozi bufite amabwiriza yo gukaraba intoki ku rubuga rwa interineti ku mugaragaro.
Iperereza ryakorewe ku buryo bukwiriye na Hitby n'abandi.
Imashini z'ubucuruzi zishobora gupima no kwemeza isuku y'intoki, niba hagisabwa kwerekana uburyo bwo guhanagura.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima rivuga ko hari "ibihe bitanu" byo gukaraba intoki:
Nyuma yo guhura n'amaraso.
Mbere yo gukora igikorwa cyo gusukura mikorobe,
Nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi. Ibikoresho byongera isabune (ibikoresho by'imiti cyangwa isabune ya antimicrobial) bitanga ibikorwa byo kwica binyuze mu gukaraba intoki.
Nk'igikorwa cyo kwica gishobora gutinda kubera kubagwa cyangwa mu byiciro by'umubiri bifite umubare munini w'abanduye.
Mikorobe zose zigomba gukurwaho.
Iki gikorwa gisaba gukaraba intoki no gukaraba intoki kugeza zumye, akenshi mu minota 2-6 gusa.
Gukaraba intoki igihe kirekire (iminota 10) ntabwo ari ngombwa.
Mu gihe cyo gukaraba, amazi yo hejuru agomba kurindwa kugaruka ku maboko.
Iyo umaze gukaraba intoki, usukura intoki ukoresheje umwenda w'isuku kandi ukambara umwenda w'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo ukwirakwize mikorobe bigabanuke, ni byiza ko ukaraba intoki cyangwa ukoresha umuti wica intoki mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'udukoko mu bitaro, byagaragaye ko ingufu zo gukaraba intoki ari 20% by'izisanzwe. Ariko ngo izo ngamba zari nke cyane kuko umubare w'izisanzwe wakomezaga kwiyongera ugera kuri 35%.
Gukaraba intoki n'isabune isanzwe bitera inshuro eshatu indwara ziterwa n'indwara z'ibyorezo ziterwa n'ibyokurya ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki n'isabune. Kugereranya gukaraba intoki n'isabune y'indwara z'ibyorezo mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 bigaragaza ko gukaraba intoki n'inzoga byagabanyije ubwandu bwa bagiteri ku kigero cya 26% ugereranyije n'isabune y'indwara z'ibyorezo.
Ariko isabune n'amazi bifite ingaruka nziza kurusha umuti wica intoki z'inzoga mu kugabanya ibicurane bya H1N1. Virusi na fungus ya Clostridium bacterium ku ntoki. Ibikorwa byo kunoza isuku y'intoki mu nzego z'ubuzima bishobora guteza imbere uburezi ku itsinda ryo gukaraba intoki, kongera ibisubizo by'inzoga zo kwica intoki, no kwandika no kwibutsa itsinda.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi burakenewe ku bikorwa bifite ingaruka nziza mu kugenzura ubuvuzi butandukanye.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki n'isabuni byatangiye kugaragara nk'uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo kugera ku buzima bwiza, ndetse no ku ifunguro ryiza.
Nyamara, kubura amazi meza, isabune cyangwa ibikoresho byo gukaraba intoki mu ngo z'abaturage, mu mashuri no mu kazi byateje ikibazo cyo gushyiraho imyitwarire yo gukaraba intoki ku isi.
Urugero, mu bice byinshi by'icyaro bya Afurika, udukingirizo two gukaraba intoki hafi y'ubwiherero bwa bwite n'ubw'abaturage ntiduhari, nubwo hari uburyo buhendutse bwo gukora udukingirizo two gukaraba intoki.
Ariko kandi, gukaraba intoki nabi bishobora gutera indwara y'ubuhumekero bitewe no kubura isabune n'amazi.
Kwiyongera no gushyigikira gukaraba intoki n'isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro ya politiki no kongera ubumenyi ku nyungu zo gukaraba intoki no kuba ingeso ndende mu baturage.
Kugira ngo ibyo bikore neza, hakenewe kugenzura no gusuzuma.
Gusuzuma ubushakashatsi 70 bwagaragaje ko imikoreshereze y'imikorere y'abaturage igira ingaruka nziza mu gukangurira abantu gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikennye, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bwo kwamamaza imikorere y'abaturage bufite ingaruka nke. Urugero rw'ikoreshwa ry'imikoreshereze y'intoki mu mashuri muri gahunda ya "Inzira y'inyenyeri eshatu" ya UNICEF, ikangurira amashuri gufata ingamba z'ubukangurambaga, mu rwego rwo kwizeza abanyeshuri ko bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki mu gihe hari ibindi bisabwa.
Iyo amanota make cyane yatanzwe, amashuri ashobora guhindurwa kuva ku nyenyeri imwe kugeza kuri eshatu.
Gushyiraho ibigo by'isuku y'amaboko bishobora kuba kimwe mu bikorwa byo kongera isuku y'amaboko byakozwe mu kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'abana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo gukaraba intoki bugamije guhindura imyitwarire, nk'ingaruka z'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-2020, UNICEF yashyize hanze emoji yo gukaraba intoki.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe na bumwe bwagaragaje ingaruka zo gukaraba intoki mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere aho guhuza n'ikoreshwa rya DALY bibujijwe.
Icyakora, isuzuma ryakozwe ryemeje ko kongera isabune mu gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kurusha amazi n'ibindi bikoresho by'isuku.
Ingaruka zo gukaraba intoki ku buzima bw'abantu - cyane cyane ku bantu bari mu mimerere iteje akaga nk'ababyeyi babyaye cyangwa abasirikare bakomerekeye mu bitaro - byatangajwe bwa mbere mu kinyejana cya 19 n'abashakashatsi babiri mu gusukura intoki: umuganga w'Umunyahongiriya Ignaz Semmelweis wakoreraga i Vienne, Austria na Florence Nightingale, washinze uburyo bw'ubuvuzi bw'icyongereza.
Icyo gihe abantu benshi bari bacyizera ko indwara ziterwa n'impumuro mbi zitwa impumuro mbi.
Mu myaka ya 1980, indwara ziterwa n'ibiribwa n'ubumenyi ku ndwara ziterwa n'indwara zatumye Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara gikoresha cyane gukaraba intoki nk'uburyo bukomeye bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'indwara.
Icyorezo cya virusi itera SIDA cyateye mu 2009 n'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu 2020 byateje ikibazo cyo kumenya akamaro ko gukaraba intoki n'isabune mu bihugu byinshi mu kwirinda indwara zandura.
