Gutegeka ibyago byo mu kazi biterwa na COVID-19
Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19 ni gahunda yo gushyiraho ingamba z'umutekano n'ubuzima mu rwego rwo kugenzura ibyago byo kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura neza impanuka mu kazi biterwa n'aho umuntu akorera n'inshingano ye, bitewe n'ibyago byo kwandura mu isoko, ubukana bw'indwara mu baturage n'ibyago by'ibintu by'umukozi bishobora gutuma adakomera ku kurwanya COVID-19.
Nk'uko byemejwe na OSHA, ibyago byo gukora nabi ku kazi ni bike cyane ku baturage no ku bakozi, bityo ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda indwara zatangajwe, zirimo gukaraba intoki no gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye cyangwa bafite ibibazo byo guhumeka, isuku ya buri gihe no kurwanya indwara zanduza ahantu bakorera.
Ibyago by'ibanze birimo gusaba guhagarika guhura n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe no guhanahana amakuru cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibi birimo abakozi bafatanya n'abaturage muri rusange nk'amashuri, ahantu hakorerwa imirimo y'inganda z'ubucuruzi buhambaye ndetse n'ibigo bimwe na bimwe by'indege.
Gutegeka ibyago kuri iri tsinda, hamwe n'uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo guhumeka neza ukoresheje imashini igezweho yo guhumeka n'indindinduramatwara ya pome no kugira ibikoresho byihariye byo kwirinda mu gihe umuntu afite COVID-19.
OSHA ifata abakozi bo mu byumba by'ubuvuzi n'ibyumba by'abapfuye bafite ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 nk'abari mu bihe bikomeye, kandi ibyago birushaho kwiyongera iyo umukozi akoresheje imashini zituma habaho umwuka mwiza cyangwa akorakoranya ibipimo by'abantu bakekwaho COVID-19 cyangwa abanduye.
Gutegeka neza ibyago ku bakozi bakora mu ishami ry'ubwubatsi bwo kugenzura nk'ibyumba byo guhanahana umwuka w'umuvuduko utagira ingufu n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'umuntu ku giti cye bikwiye akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutaba ku kazi kubera ko bashobora kurwara, kubera ko bagomba kwita ku bandi cyangwa kubera ko batinya kwandura.
Abafatanyabikorwa mu bucuruzi bashobora guhindura icyifuzo cy'ibicuruzwa basabwe n'impamvu yabyo (urugero, gucuruza igihe abantu baje guhaha cyangwa gutanga cyangwa gucuruza mu gace).
Mu minsi ya vuba aha, amato y'amakamyo mu turere twibasiwe na COVID-19 ashobora guhagarikwa. Kwitegura icyorezo no gutegura guhangana bishobora gukoreshwa mu gukora ibikorwa by'ubwirinzi.
Imigambi igaragaza ibipimo by'ibyago bijyanye n'aho virusi ikorera n'imirimo ikorerwa, harimo inkomoko y'ubwandu n'uburyo bwo gushyiraho ibintu bituma ibyago byiyongera mu rugo no mu baturage, hamwe n'ibintu by'ibyago ku muntu ku giti cye nk'imyaka y'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara zidakira.
Bavuga kandi ko bagomba gushyiraho ingamba zo guhangana n'ibiza no gutegura ibisubizo by'ibiza bishobora gutuma icyorezo cyongera.
Imyiteguro n'imigambi y'indwara zandura bishobora kuba ikibazo cy'amabwiriza y'igihugu n'ay'igihugu.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo ni ukugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu itsinda, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byo kurwara indwara zikomeye no kugabanya ingaruka ku bandi barwayi.
Uburemere bw'iki cyorezo buvugwa mu baturage bagizweho ingaruka n'iki cyorezo.
Kuzamura ibihombo ni igitekerezo gikoreshwa cyane mu bikorwa byo kurinda no kurinda itsinda ry'ibihombo bigenzurwa n'ibikorwa.
Iyo ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora kugenzurwa, ingamba z'ingenzi ni ingufu z'ubwubatsi zikurikirwa n'iz'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
Gutegeka kwa tekinike birimo kwirinda abakozi guhura n'ibiza bidaturutse ku myitwarire y'umukozi kandi bishobora kuba umuti mwiza cyane wo gushyira mu bikorwa.
Gucunga ubuyobozi ni impinduka mu mikorere y'akazi cyangwa ingamba zisaba ko abakozi bagira icyo bakora.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwa bwite (PPE) bifatwa nk'ibidakora cyane nk'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibikoresho by'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda ubwandu.
Ubwoko bwose bwa PPE bugomba kugenwa hakurikijwe ibyago by'abakozi, ku rugero rukwiriye (urugero: ibibazo byo guhumeka), ku buryo bukwiriye, ku buryo bwemewe n'amategeko, ku buryo burambye, ku buryo bushobora gukurikiranwa, aho bikenewe, ku buryo bwemewe, ku buryo bwemewe, ku buryo bwemewe, ku buryo bwemewe, ku buryo bwemewe, ku buryo bwemewe, ku buryo bukwiriye, ku buryo bufite gahunda yo kwirinda kwanduza.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye gishinzwe Ubuzima n'Umutekano (OSHA), ibyago byo ku kazi biri hasi cyane ku bantu muri rusange no ku bakozi bo mu bigo.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kwirinda ubwandu bwatanzwe ku kazi kose ko gukaraba intoki cyane no gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo niba barwaye cyangwa bafite ibibazo byo guhumeka birimo inkorora na piscine, gutanga isuku n'umukungugu, kwitegura kuvugana kure cyangwa guhinduranya amasaha y'akazi niba ari ngombwa, kuburira abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho hamwe no kwagura gahunda zo gusukura no kurwanya indwara zanduza ahantu bakorera.
Gushishikariza abantu kumenya no kwirinda abantu banduye ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) gitanga inama ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso baguma mu rugo kugeza igihe bazaba barakize icyorezo cy'imvune, ibimenyetso by'imvune n'ibindi bimenyetso mu gihe cy'amasaha 24 nta muti cyangwa imiti, kandi igihe icyorezo kizaba cyaragabanutse, bemerera abakozi kuguma mu rugo kugira ngo barebe abagize imiryango yabo barwaye, n'abakozi bazi neza ingamba.
