Abakozi bari mu bantu bafite ibyago byinshi ntibakunze gusaba gukoresha ibyuma byo guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye ku kibuga cy'indege, ingamba zifatika zirakorwa mu kurinda abakozi n'abagenzi harimo gutandukanya umurwayi n'abandi bantu mu ntera ya metero 6 no gushyira umuntu mu itsinda ryo kwita ku murwayi, guha umurwayi agapfukamunwa cyangwa gusaba umurinzi w'umunwa n'umunwa igihe arira cyangwa asoma.
Itsinda ry'abakozi bagomba kwambara uturindantoki tw'ubuvuzi mu gihe bakorana n'umunyeshuri urwaye cyangwa bakorana n'amazi yo mu mubiri cyangwa imyanda, kandi bakongera ibikoresho byo kwirinda mu gihe umunyeshuri arwaye afite igifu kidakira cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Ibikoresho by'ubufasha n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bigomba gutekerwa mu mufuka wa plastiki kandi imyanda igomba gusukurwa no gukingirwa. Ku masoko y'ibikoresho, harimo n'ingendo z'ubucuruzi n'ubwato bw'abagenzi, kugenzura ibyangiritse birasaba gusubika ingendo igihe urwaye cyangwa ukirinda wenyine no kubwira ikigo nderabuzima cyabakozi b'ubwato niba hari umuntu ufite ubwandu cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso ku bwato.
