Iyo nta mbaraga zihagije zikorwa mu kugabanya itumanaho, ingamba zo kwirinda abantu ku buryo bw'imishyikirano zishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa nko kwanga ingendo, amateraniro n'andi materaniro manini nk'amasomo y'ubuvuzi cyangwa amateraniro y'idini cyangwa gusangira muri cafeteria, kongera igihe cyo gufungura no gutegura ingendo n'ikiruhuko cy'abanyeshuri, no kugabanya ingendo zidakenewe no gukoresha ahantu ho kwa muganga ku bana bafite ibimenyetso bya grippe.
Iyo hari ubwandu buhambaye mu baturage, nubwo hari uburyo bwo gutandukanya abantu, birashoboka ko hashyirwaho ikiruhuko cy'amasomo. Ku mategeko y'ubuyobozi yo gushyiraho ingamba zikomeye z'ibikorwa bya buri munsi, ibyago by'ubuzima bwihuse bifatwa nkibike na CDC.
