Niba hari guhura cyane mugihe cyumutwaro uteje akaga, abakozi bagomba gusukura imirunga n'ibikoresho byimodoka no kubikoresha kugirango bakoreshe, bakoresha ibyuma byo gusukura no gusukura intoki, no gukoresha ibikorwa bisanzwe byo gusukura. Koresha PPE nkeya no gusukura no gusukura imyenda.
