ACE2 ni ikinyabutabire gifasha mu kuvura indwara z'ubuhumekero, mu maraso, mu myanya y'ubuhumekero no mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
ACE2 ihagarika ibikorwa bya ACE-interactions by'indwara ya angiotensin-binding enzymes mu kugabanya umuvuduko w'indwara ya Angiotensin-binding na Angiotensin-1-7 mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi. ACE2 kandi ifasha nk'inzugi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo zimwe na zimwe za koronavirusi.
Ubwoko bwa muntu bwa enzyme akenshi buvugwa nka hACE2.
Zinc-metal-containing Zinc-twin angiotensin enzymes ziterwa n'uruhu rw'imbere rw'utugingo n'utundi duce duto cyane.
Poroteyine ACE2 igizwe n'umuvuduko wa N wa poroteyine ya peptidase M2 hamwe n'umuvuduko wa C uhuza poroteyine ya amino acide.
ACE ni ubwoko bumwe bw'indwara ya I, ifite enzyme ikora ku murandasi ku mubiri w'ibihaha ndetse no mu bindi bice by'umubiri.
Icyuma cy'ingenzi cyitwa ACE2 cyasimbuwe n'indwara ya SIDA, cyitwa shades, kikaba ari igipimo cy'indwara y'ibicurane mu maraso, kigasohoka mu maraso, kigashyirwa mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu ngingo nyinshi: ACE2 ifatanye n'utugingo tw'ingirabuzimafatizo, cyane cyane uturemangingo tw'umura, uturemangingo two mu mara mato, uturemangingo tw'amaraso n'utw'amaraso, n'utugingo tw'umusatsi woroshye mu ngingo nyinshi.
ACE2 ni indi mRNA iboneka mu gice cy'imbere cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'iburyo cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'iburyo cy'ubwonko, no mu gice cy'ibumoso cy'ubwonko.
Inshingano ya mbere ya ACE2 ni ukugabanya ACE.
ACE ihindura ingano y'umusemburo wa angiotensin imwe mu maraso mu maraso.
ACE2 ikora isuku ya carboxyl-termial amino acid phenylalanine ikura mu anigotensin II (Asp-Arg-Bal-Tyr-IIe-His-Pro-Phe) maze ikayivanga na angiotensin (1 - 7, (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Lle-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora kandi kwanduza ibindi bintu byinshi by'ibinyabutabire nka -[des-Arg9] bradykinin, apelin neurotensin, dynorp hin A, ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi itegeka uburyo bwo kwimura aside ya SLC6A19 kandi kandi igaragara no mu ndwara ya Hartnap.
Kimwe na poroteyine y'umuvuduko, ACE2 ikora nk'ahantu h'ingenzi ho kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe, urugero nka HcoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, gusimbuza S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 ku mutera ACE2 ku mibiri y'ingirabuzimafatizo, bituma habaho impinduka zikomeye mu buryo bw'imikorere ya virusi na enzymes mu mubiri.
Bivugwa ko kugabanya ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo, bishobora gufasha kurwanya iyi ndwara.
Icyakora, hari imiryango imwe n'imwe y'abahanga n'abakora imyitozo ngororamubiri bakomeza gutanga inama yo kugabanya ACE no kugabanya ARB.
Igishushanyo mbonera cyakozwe n'ishyirahamwe ry'ubushakashatsi n'iterambere cyasohotse ku ya 11 Nyakanga 2020, cyerekana ko "ikoreshwa rya ACE ryatewe imbere hamwe n'ibanga rya 34% kugabanya ibyago byo guhura n'ibiza mu gihe cy'imiyoborere".
Byongeye kandi, "ibyago byo kurwara indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha byari bike mu barwayi bavurwa ACE inhibitors, aho kuba byinshi mu barwayi barwaye indwara y'ibihaha, cyane cyane abafite ikibazo cy'umutima udakora neza.
