Australia na New Zealand byombi byashyigikiye gahunda ya Singapore yo gukurikirana no gukurikirana Bluetooth. Uburusiya bushaka gushyiraho gahunda yo gukurikirana abarwayi basanzwemo COVID-19 baba i Moscou, igamije kwemeza ko abarwayi batava mu rugo.
