Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'impungenge z'uko porogaramu za coronavirus zishobora gutakaza cyangwa zikabangamira abantu, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongera porogaramu zimeze nka coronavirus ku bubiko bwayo bwa AOL.
Google na Amazon byashyize hamwe mu buryo nk'ubwo bwo kubuza.
Abateye ku giti cyabo bagaragaje impungenge ku bibazo by'ibanze byo kugenzura ikoreshwa rya coronavirus, by'umwihariko niba ibikorwa remezo by'ubushakashatsi byubatswe neza kugirango bikemure coronavirus kandi bigire uruhare mu guhangana n'akaga.
Umuryango mpuzamahanga w'ubushakashatsi n'imiryango 100 yatangaje icyo bise ko ari ugusaba ko ibyo bisobanuro bigabanywa.
Amashyirahamwe yatangaje ibintu umunani bisabwa ku mishinga ya leta:
Gushyira mu gaciro bigomba kuba "amategeko yose. Ni ngombwa kandi biringaniye".
Gushyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda no kwirinda;
Gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba bihagaritswe kubera COVID-19;
Umutekano n'ubuziranenge bw'amakuru bigomba kurindwa kandi bigaragazwa n'ibimenyetso byerekana ko bikingiwe;
Digital Monitoring igomba kwirinda kwangiza ivangura n'ivangura;
Gutanga amakuru ku muntu wa gatatu bigomba gusobanurwa mu mategeko;
Hakwiye kuba n'abagabo bashinzwe umutekano kugira ngo basubize abantu bahura n'ibibazo no kurengera uburenganzira bw'abaturage babo;
Uruhare rw'ingenzi rwasabwe n'abashoramari bose "bafite aho babogamiye", harimo impuguke mu by'ubuzima rusange n'imiryango itishoboye. Umunyamakuru wa Reporters Without Borders (CCC) na RSF na bo bemeye ko nta kosa ryakorwaga.
Gahunda yatanzwe na Google na Apple yagombaga gukemura ikibazo cy'ubugenzuzi bukomeje binyuze mu gukuraho uburyo bwo kugenzura muri sisitemu yo kuyobora terefone mugihe bitakiri ngombwa.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe bikoresha interineti ishingiye ku gukurikirana aho kurinda aho gukoresha porogaramu, gukuraho byombi bisaba gukuramo porogaramu, no kubura ubushobozi bwo gukurikirana.
Muri Isirayeli, interineti igenzurwa yaremewe.
Interineti ishingiye ku gukemura ibibazo byo kugera ku makuru y'ahantu handuye ifite ikibazo cyo guhisha neza imiterere.
Nubwo, ntabwo ari ngombwa ko sisitemu zose na seriveri z'ibanze zifite ubushobozi bwo gukoresha amakuru y'ahantu bwite; hari uburyo bwinshi bwo kurinda ubuzima bwite bwakozwe bukoresha seriveri z'ibanze gusa kugirango zitumvikane (reba ingingo ikurikira).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hakoreshejwe uburyo butari bushingiye kuri porogaramu mu gukora igenzura ry'itumanaho.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu runaka, sisitemu yakusanyije amakuru y'ibanze aturuka ahantu hatandukanye nk'amakuru y'ibanze ya mudasobwa zigendanwa n'amakuru y'ikarita ikoreshwa, hanyuma ayashyira hamwe kugirango abone inyandiko y'ibanze y'abantu banduye.
Uretse gukoresha aya makuru kugira ngo amenye amakuru y'imibanire y'abantu, leta nayo yashyize ahagaragara amakuru yayo, ibintu bimwe na bimwe byemewe kubera intera iri hagati y'amakuru y'abantu ku giti cyabo n'amategeko amaze guhinduka nyuma y'ihirikwa rya MERS muri icyo gihugu.
Aya makuru ashobora kuboneka ku mugaragaro binyuze muri porogaramu nyinshi na website. Ibihugu nka Ubudage byashyizeho uburyo bwo gukoresha ibigo by'ububiko n'uburyo bwo kurinda ubuzima bwite.
