Ibiza byinshi ku isi mu 2020, bizatuma ibikorwa byishoramari n'ubushakashatsi mu iterambere ry'umuti w'inkorano.
Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo gukoresha ibinyabuzima byemewe mu gukora umuti wa SARS-CoV-2.
Muri Mata, CEPI yatangaje ibisabwa by'ibanze byo guteza imbere ububiko bwa Peyote birimo umuvuduko, ubushobozi bwo gukora, ibikoresho bitunganywa neza no guhuza isi yose.
Muri Mata, abahanga mu bya siyansi ba CEPI batangaje ko hari ikoranabuhanga 10 ry'urubuga rwihariye rwari mu bushakashatsi no mu iterambere mu ntangiriro za 2020 mu gukora urukingo rukora neza kuri COVID-19.
Ibigo byinshi by'intego z'iterambere mu isesengura ry'ubuzima 1 birimo:
Amashinyaguro ya nucleic acids (DNA na RNA) (icyiciro cya 1 cy'abashakashatsi n'abashakashatsi: moderna, mRNA-1273)
Virusi yo mu cyiciro cya 1 n'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus yo mu cyiciro cya 5.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'abahanga ba CEPI muri Mata, inganda 115 zose zatoranijwe mu byiciro bya mbere by'iterambere, 78 zashyizwe hamwe nk'imishinga ikora (79 nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikigo cya Milkin), izindi 37 zatangajwe, ariko zitangazwa n'amakuru make y'abaturage (yaba yashyizwe mu bikorwa cyangwa yashyizwe ku murongo).
Icyiciro cya 1-2 cy'igerageza gitanga ubuziranenge bw'ibanze n'igerageza ryo kurwanya indwara, akenshi rigenzurwa ku buryo bw'ibanze, ritanga imiti idafite ingaruka mbi kandi ku mpande zombi, mu gihe hagaragazwa imiti mu buryo bwimbitse kandi bwimbitse.
Icyiciro cya 3 cy'igerageza gisanzwe kirimo abitabiriye benshi, harimo itsinda ry'ubugenzuzi n'igerageza ry'ingaruka za cocaine mu gukumira indwara mu gihe hakurikiranwa ingaruka mbi z'imiti.
