Kwiga inkingo muri buri buryo bisaba ko zigeragezwa ku mutekano n'ubushobozi. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, igeragezwa rya mbere ry'ubuvuzi bw'inkingo ryatangiye ku bantu bane bitangiye muri Seattle.
Iyo virusi ifite kode y'ubwoko butari bubi yakuwe muri virusi itera iyo ndwara.Ibikorwa byo kongera umubiri bigaragazwa nk'inzitizi ikomeye mu iterambere ry'iyo virusi ya 2-SARS-CoV, ariko ibi biracyari impaka.
Ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 byakozwe muri Mata 2020.
Ibizamini birindwi byasuzumwe kandi imiti yemewe mu kuvura malaria, harimo ibizamini bine bya hydrochloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa bwagombaga kuba ku miti ya virusi, hamwe n'igerageza ry'ibice icyenda bya gatatu bya Redisceptor mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bigomba gutangazwa mu mpera za Mata.
Iterambere ry'ikigo nderabuzima cyo gusuzuma vuba urukingo rwa COVID-19 n'impuguke mu buvuzi birakomeje, nk'uko byari bimeze muri Mata 2020. Hari imiti ya virusi itera SIDA yasuzumwe mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo Remdesivir na Hydrochlorothiazine, Lopinvir/Ritonavir na Lopinvir/Ritonavir ifatanywe na beta inhibitors.
Hari ibimenyetso by'agateganyo by'ingaruka za Remdesivir, nk'uko byari bimeze muri Gicurasi 2020.
Iterambere mu by'ubuzima ryagaragaye mu barwayi bavurwa indwara z'ihungabana bahabwa umuti wa Remdesivir.
Icyiciro cya gatatu cy'igeragezwa ry'ibigo by'ubuzima cyakozwe muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Chloroquine yari isanzwe ikoreshwa mu kuvura malariya, yageragejwe mu Bushinwa mu kwezi kwa kabiri 2020 hamwe n'ibisubizo by'ingenzi by'ibanze.
Nubwo bimeze bityo ariko, hari aho bahuriye no gusuzuma ubushakashatsi.
Leta ya Korea n'ishami ry'ubuzima ry'Ubushinwa byemeje ko chlorquine ikoreshwa.
Nubwo, ikigo cya Wuhan cyo gukora ubushakashatsi kuri virusi, mu gihe gitanga inama y'ifunguro rimwe ku munsi rya gramu imwe, kivuga ko kurenza ifunguro rimwe ry'ibiryo bibiri ari ibintu biteje akaga kandi bishobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Gicurasi 2020, FDA yatangaje ko ikoresha mu buryo butunguranye hydrochlorothiazin na chloroquine mu gufata ibyemezo byemewe n'amategeko ku buryo bwo kuvura abantu bafite COVID-19. Ubuyobozi bwa karindwi bw'ikigo cya interferon (ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri ku virusi), ravavirin cyangwa amifenovir ku mikoreshereze yo kurwanya COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze avuga ko indyo ikungahaye kuri ribavirin ari ingenzi cyane ku bantu barwaye SARS-CoV-2 mu cyumba.
Nitazoxanide yagaragajwe ko ikoreshwa mu kongera ikoreshwa rya In vivo nyuma yo kugaragaza kugabanya ubukana bwa SARS-CoV-2. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko poroteyine ya mbere ya sisitemu itunganywa na TMPRSS2 (TMPRSS2) ari yo shingiro ryo kwinjira muri SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhura na ACE2.
Ibizamini bya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na antibiyotike cyangwa nta antibiyotike bifite aho bigarukira bituma umuryango w'abaganga udashobora kwemeza imiti idafite ubushakashatsi bwimbitse. Oseltamivir ntabwo ibuza SARS-CoV-2 kandi nta ruhare ruzwi igira mu kuvura COVID-19.
Kwirukana cytokine bishobora kuba ikibazo mu gihe cya COVID-19 ikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira imiterere yo kurwanya cytokine. Ikoreshwa rya Tocilizumab ryashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo Mpuzamahanga y'Ubuzima ya Sinon nyuma y'uko ubushakashatsi buto bwuzuye.
Ni igerageza ry'ibizamini bibiri byakozwe ku rwego mpuzamahanga mu Butaliyani nyuma y'uko abantu banduye bagaragaye bafite uburwayi bukomeye.
Iyo bifatanyije n'ibipimo by'amaraso bigamije kumenya ikibazo cy'imyakura, bifasha mu gusubiza ibibazo, bishobora no gutuma abantu bamwe na bamwe barwaye bapfa.
Cytokine receptor antagonist-6 yemejwe na FDA hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwo kuvura ibimenyetso by'indwara ya Steroid cytocine ikora ku murwayi ukomeye, CAR T cell therapy 2017.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya ihamye cyangwa ihamye yemeza ko tocilizumab ari umuti mwiza wa CRS.
Kwimura no guhinduranya za antibodies zikoranywe imbaraga n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bw'abantu bakize COVID-19 ku bantu bakenewe cyane mu buryo bworoshye bwo kwirinda indwara zidakumira.
Iki gikorwa cyageragejwe kuri SARS nta musaruro ufatika.
Virusi y'ubwoko bumwe ni uburyo bwo gukora ibivugwa ko umuti wa SARS-CoV-2 ushobora kurwanya ubudahangarwa.
Ibindi byuma ariko, nk'umubiri ushingiye ku cyotoxicity cyangwa ibikorwa byo guhosha bakteri bishobora kuba bishoboka.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura antibody zidakora, urugero, gukoresha antibody z'umwuga za monolonal biri mu nzira.
Ibikoresho byo gukusanya plasma y'amaraso y'umwimerere, bikubiyemo poroteyine z'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize n'urukingo rw'umwihariko rwa virusi rushobora kongerwa kugira ngo rushobore gukwirakwira vuba.
Indwara ziterwa na koronavirusi ni itsinda ry'indwara zisanzwe ziterwa n'ibimenyetso.
